This package has VyOS avahi - mDNS/DNS-SD configuration templates and scripts.

Available configuration nodes:

service {
    mdns {
        reflector
        repeater {
            interface eth0
            interface eth2
            interface eth4
        }
    }
}

Configuration node files/scripts have been copied from 
EdgeOS v1.9.7+hotfix.2.5010181.170818.0412. Thank you Ubiquity!
